external_knowledge:
- 'garden of well-fitted clothes' refers to the context of the 'well-fitting' clothes feedback;
- 'blooming averages' metaphorically represents the calculated averages of the minimum height requirements;
- 'male and female blossoms' are the metaphorical representations of the genders in the customer data;
- 'perfect suits' represents the sizes that received a 'fits well' rating.

sql:
SELECT DISTINCT b.brand_name, b.brand_description
FROM brands b
JOIN size_charts sc ON b.brand_id = sc.brand_id;

external_knowledge:
- "cast their shadows" metaphorically represents providing feedback;
- "realm of size feedback" refers to the size_feedback table where customers provide their opinion on the fit of garments;
- "yet to receive a verdict on the comfort of their apparel" means that the fit_rating for these customers is null, indicating no fit evaluation has been recorded.

sql:
SELECT p.product_name, sf.fit_rating, sf.comments
FROM products p
JOIN size_feedback sf ON p.product_id = sf.product_id;
